{"tid":1174261,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好心你班反修例嘅仆街唔好成日標題黨","createTime":"2019-05-27T16:54:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T06:42:36.000Z","uid":68851,"like":24,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1b56358be7f3c399c7fcf11c01e46cefce8f4474","tid":1174261,"uid":68851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T16:54:40.000Z","msg":"利申咗先：反送中 6月9會去<br />\n<br />\n即是咁 你哋喺每個post都留叫人支持 <br />\n叫人6月9出席 都唔覺大問題 因為都只係一個CM <br />\n唔影響討論<br />\n<br />\n但好撚心你班撚屌咪鳩成日標題黨啦 成日呃鳩人入去 入到去根本唔係嗰回事 同標題完全唔撚一樣<br />\n<br />\n例子：<br />\n[多圖]反修例街站啲女真心正<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1173928\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1173928</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n估唔到波台都有咁靚女既絲打..<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1173522\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1173522</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n同卡勞成鳩日呃人入去睇隻麻友G<br />\n同印度仔呃人入去睇男人婆<br />\n有乜撚嘢分別？屌你老母<br />\n唔好意思 原來有 你哋連女圖都冇張<br />\n<br />\n我一心入去想打個J 褲都除埋 女圖都冇張<br />\n唔好話咩打少個J 香港存亡乜柒<br />\n6月9會去 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n支持還支持<br />\n但你班仆街成日咁呃鳩人好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50834611498f28e9b4e5d50100cea5d583a318fb","tid":1174261,"uid":5883,"like":0,"dislike":20,"score":-20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T16:57:17.000Z","msg":"对呀"},{"pid":"fd87ad53aa8cdfe2dfcb894e8f7a99b36be2cefc","tid":1174261,"uid":68851,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"50834611498f28e9b4e5d50100cea5d583a318fb","tid":1174261,"uid":5883,"like":0,"dislike":20,"score":-20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T16:57:17.000Z","msg":"对呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T17:00:12.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n仲上連登？返去同維尼爭蜜糖啦"},{"pid":"892c307bc5746bb0d6ea7bade796409bb4d9a62f","tid":1174261,"uid":253340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T17:14:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"495edf32b5e4628928cca5eec5349d20d78afad9","tid":1174261,"uid":68851,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T17:22:01.000Z","msg":"其實而家上得連登 冇七成都有八成嘅post都講緊<br />\n反送中 6月9 街站<br />\n<br />\n再講會㩒入去嘅 一係關心時事 關心香港<br />\n再唔係就五毛<br />\n<br />\n都唔明點解仲要玩標題黨呃鳩人入去<br />\n真係好撚乞人憎<br />\n<br />\n要標題黨就去Facebook/其他forum呃人睇好過啦<br />\n其他平台差唔多冇人關心6月9咁濟"},{"pid":"39f60bd9b0954a65e04e492c2d3dc80f4db1b051","tid":1174261,"uid":68851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T06:35:58.000Z","msg":"【有片】城大學生比人影到係hall扑野唔拉窗簾<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1174717\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1174717</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母"},{"pid":"3a816888a9ce2867d14f0f56371744485412a65f","tid":1174261,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39f60bd9b0954a65e04e492c2d3dc80f4db1b051","tid":1174261,"uid":68851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T06:35:58.000Z","msg":"【有片】城大學生比人影到係hall扑野唔拉窗簾<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1174717\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1174717</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T06:37:08.000Z","msg":"三毛嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59ba379a4ddf48aa48e3c24a3cbeae1bd1c94e87","tid":1174261,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T06:38:30.000Z","msg":"贊成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過上面其中一個，阿古路五毛嚟<br />\n<br />\n哩個既樓主都似係（做開屎為打手）<br />\n<br />\n【有片】城大學生比人影到係hall扑野唔拉窗簾<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1174717\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1174717</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"db6ff247b00e9678bf10447c337a049af6ee9b91","tid":1174261,"uid":68851,"like":3,"disl